Template:
  W=WINDOW/F

Specification: 
WINDOW=<Window>    Where Window is a file name specifying the name of the
                   window to snapshot.  If not specified this will snapshot
                   the current window.

Callable via:
  ARexx, internally

Example:
  SnapshotWindow
  SnapshotWindow SYS:Prefs

@endnode

